  "description": "A stunning panoramic view of a cityscape bathed in the golden and orange hues of a sunset. The sun, a bright orb, peeks through a layer of clouds near the horizon, casting a warm glow over the landscape. Below, a sprawling urban area with closely packed buildings stretches towards the water, while distant hills and mountains form a soft backdrop. A long bridge is visible extending into the water. The foreground features a lush, dark green treeline adding depth to the composition. The clouds themselves are dramatically lit, with shades of orange, yellow, and even deep red, creating a textured and dynamic sky.",
